secubox-newsbin (1.0.0-1~bookworm1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Initial release.
  * SABnzbd container management (Docker/Podman).
  * Features:
    - NZB download management (URL and file upload)
    - Download queue with pause/resume controls
    - Usenet server configuration
    - Category-based organization
    - Download history and statistics
    - Container install/start/stop/restart/update
    - Backup and restore functionality
    - P31 Phosphor light theme with yellow accent

